12 October 2005Media are invited to attend a media briefing following the Cabinet meeting held in Pretoria today. The briefing will be led by the CEO of Government Communications (GCIS), Joel Netshitenzhe. The details are as follows:Date: 12 October 2005 Time: 16h00 Venue: Room 710, Midtown Building, Cnr. of Prinsloo and Vermeulen Streets, Pretoria CentralRSVP Nikhil Bramdaw Cell: 083 777 6827Lindo Nkomonde Cell: 082 875 9631NB: There will be a video link-up from Pretoria to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)